{
  "stem": "4146.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some people left, went to the United States.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Some went to Israel, when they could, when they got the money to go.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He killed them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Put them in, in concentration, and they killed them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What were you doing at the age of 15 and 16?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, I was learning as a carpenter, because I want to go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So were you saving money?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I want to have it, a-- something that I can survive in Israel.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A trade, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I was like to go, but they close up and they don't let that go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, and I went to my brothers over there, and I helped them out too.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I should, I should make it some-- a little more money.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We should have it to make a living.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "20.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They drafted me to the army.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First of all, we-- I was a Jabotinsky.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We used to have it the same schools, like the army's.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we want to go to Israel, we want to fight for our country.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But still, a lot of them, of them, we couldn't go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In 1939, end of 1939, when I was in the army until 1939-- no, almost 1940.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "End of 1939, we lost it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Polish army was like-- they lose it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They couldn't do nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in the army.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was shot here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A little there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Germans.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, at the beginning, sometimes we had some of them from Wolbrom, very orthodox boys, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Religious.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they were in the army, and the food they don't eat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because it was not kosher.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I give them bread, and they give me the soup.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I changed.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because I want them to have it.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
